OL,8,     Foperation spirals into a standoff.
OL,9,     FAnd officers head to remote
OL,10,     Fwoodland, where a wanted man is
OL,11,     Fbelieved to be in hiding.
OL,12,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FWith drink driving still a major
OL,14,     Fcause of serious collisions, cops
