OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FExploring how criminals use some
OL,7,     Fof the Derbyshire's fastest roads,
OL,8,     Fincluding the M1. In this episode,
OL,9,     Fit takes six units from two police
OL,10,     Fforces to stop a suspected cloned
OL,11,     Fvan.
OL,12,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FInterceptor Spike takes the lead
OL,14,     Fagainst a runaway car thief in one
OL,15,     Fof the most challenging pursuits
OL,16,     Fever. Liam investigates a drug
OL,17,     Fdealing gang.
OL,18,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,19,     FJacko is forced to draw his taser,
OL,20,     Fleading to a shocking result. Liam
OL,21,     FSewell discovers a new type of
OL,22,     Fherbal pizza topping.
