OL,6,     FEden has second thoughts. Dana and
OL,7,     FAlf work together. Is Justin in
OL,8,     Fdanger?
OL,9,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FIt's a busy week at Hall Green
OL,11,     FHealth Centre as the doctors see
OL,12,     Flots of patients who are
OL,13,     Fstruggling to manage their weight.
OL,14,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,15,     FWith the computer system down, the
OL,16,     Fstaff resort to a whiteboard to
OL,17,     Fkeep track of everyone. Patients
OL,18,     Finclude two elderly men with
OL,19,     Fbreathing difficulties.
