OL,5,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FDoctors treat a non-verbal young
OL,7,     Fman in a life-threatening
OL,8,     Fneurological emergency, while a
OL,9,     Fmidwife with severe spinal pain is
OL,10,     Ffeared to have cauda equina
OL,11,     Fsyndrome after back surgery.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA builder falls from a great
OL,14,     Fheight while working in a derelict
OL,15,     Ffarm building; a car wash employee
OL,16,     Fis stabbed dangerously close to
OL,17,     Ftheir liver.
OL,18,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,19,     FA look at misbehaving lumps, from
OL,20,     Fthe biggest (13cm) to the smallest
OL,21,     Fthat the dermatologists have ever
OL,22,     Ftreated.
