OL,5,G0000 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,6,     FIn Coventry, a prolific shoplifter
OL,7,     Fis caught, and claims he steals
OL,8,     Fout of necessity. At a QD store
OL,9,     Fsomeone thinks they can get away
OL,10,     Fwith not paying for their
OL,11,     FChristmas shopping. (Ep2)
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FThis week at the Hall Green Health
OL,14,     FCentre, the doctors work to get to
OL,15,     Fthe bottom of various conditions.
OL,16,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FDr Julian Humphrey treats one
OL,18,     Fpatient with a aortic dissection,
OL,19,     Fand another with a regularly
OL,20,     Fdislocated shoulder. Documentary
OL,21,     Fseries filmed inside Barnsley
OL,22,     Fcasualty department.
